          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="flex items-start justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-canvas-soft-2 rounded-full text-mute/60 font-bold text-xs">3</span>
            <span><strong>Turn on background sound if you like</strong> to block out noise, then hit start and get into flow.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="flex items-start justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-canvas-soft-2 rounded-full text-mute/60 font-bold text-xs">4</span>
            <span><strong>Check off what you finished and reflect.</strong> Mark completed steps, log how it went, and learn from every session.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- PREMIUM FEATURE SHOWCASE -->
      <div id="features-showcase" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-20 px-2 space-y-12 scroll-mt-6">
        <div class="text-center space-y-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-body/80">Workspace capabilities</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-3 leading-[1.1]">Core features</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-body leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Just the essentials: set a goal, choose your time, and get to work — all offline, all private.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Feature 1: Focus Sessions -->
          <div class="border border-hairline rounded-sm p-4 sm:p-6 bg-canvas hover:border-hairline hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-250 flex gap-4 card-lift">
            <div class="p-3 bg-canvas-soft-2 text-mute/60 rounded-sm h-fit shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-1">Customizable focus sessions</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-body leading-relaxed">
                Choose your own work and break lengths — whether that's the classic 25/5, a deep 90-minute sprint, or something in between. Switch on ambient brown noise, white noise, or rain to help you focus, all generated right in your browser without any downloads.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 2: Goal Tracking -->
          <div class="border border-hairline rounded-sm p-4 sm:p-6 bg-canvas hover:border-purple-500/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-250 flex gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 rounded-sm h-fit shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-1">Micro-goal milestone tracking</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-body leading-relaxed">
                Set a clear intention before you start, then break big tasks into small checkpoints so you always know what's next. When your session ends, mark whether you finished, partly finished, or got stuck — and build real momentum over time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 3: Forecasting -->
          <div class="border border-hairline rounded-sm p-4 sm:p-6 bg-canvas hover:border-emerald-500/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-250 flex gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 rounded-sm h-fit shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83"/><path d="M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-1">Success analytics & forecasting</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-body leading-relaxed">
                Understand your cognitive baseline with rich analytics. Track focus durations, success curves, and completion rates. Our dashboard features a GitHub-style heatmap showing focus density and calculates success rate probability metrics to forecast future workflow success.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 4: Recovery Planning -->
          <div class="border border-hairline rounded-sm p-4 sm:p-6 bg-canvas hover:border-rose-500/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-250 flex gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-400 rounded-sm h-fit shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-1">Cognitive recovery coach</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-body leading-relaxed">
                Interrupted? Don't stress. If a focus block is skipped or marked as failed, our localized Recovery Advisor engine diagnoses the root driver (mental fatigue, ambient noise, task scope) and generates actionable recovery pacing corrections (e.g. screen-free breaks, reducing block size).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 5: Growth Reports -->
          <div class="border border-hairline rounded-sm p-4 sm:p-6 bg-canvas hover:border-amber-500/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-250 flex gap-4 md:col-span-2">
            <div class="p-3 bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 rounded-sm h-fit shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-1">Monthly performance growth reports</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-body leading-relaxed">
                Compile your locally logged activity data into a beautiful, printable PDF Performance Digest. Get personal growth analytics including focus density curves, streak timelines, achievement milestones, and personalized coaching reflections to guide your habit progression without any account setups.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-16">
      <FAQ items={faqItems} renderSchema={false} />
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- OUTCOME DISPOSAL MODAL DIALOG (Triggered when session finishes or is skipped/completed) -->
  <div id="outcome-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="outcome-modal-title" class="fixed inset-0 bg-canvas/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-[9999] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-canvas border border-hairline/40 rounded-2xl shadow-elevated overflow-hidden animate-in fade-in zoom-in-95 duration-200">
      
      <div class="p-5 border-b border-hairline flex items-center justify-between bg-canvas-soft-2/50">
        <div>
            <h2 id="outcome-modal-title" class="text-base font-bold text-ink flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-mute/60"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            How did it go?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-mute mt-0.5">Take a moment to reflect</p>
        </div>
        <button type="button" id="modal-close-x-btn" aria-label="Close outcome dialog" class="min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] flex items-center justify-center p-1 text-mute hover:text-ink rounded hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 active:scale-90 cursor-pointer">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <form id="outcome-form" class="p-5 space-y-4">
        <!-- Goal display -->
        <div class="p-3 bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline rounded-sm text-sm">
          <div class="text-mute text-sm mb-1">What you set out to do:</div>
          <div class="font-bold text-ink" id="modal-goal-text">Initialize focus layout</div>
          <div class="text-mute text-sm mt-1.5" id="modal-milestone-ratio">0 of 0 checkpoints</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Outcome Radios -->
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-mute tracking-tight">How do you feel about this session?</label>
          
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
            <!-- Completed -->
            <label class="outcome-radio-label flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-3 border border-hairline/40 rounded-xl bg-canvas text-ink text-center hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 cursor-pointer active:scale-95 transition-all">
              <input type="radio" name="outcome" value="Completed" required class="sr-only" />
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-link mb-1"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold">Completed</span>
            </label>
            
            <!-- Partial -->
            <label class="outcome-radio-label flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-3 border border-hairline/40 rounded-xl bg-canvas text-ink text-center hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 cursor-pointer active:scale-95 transition-all">
              <input type="radio" name="outcome" value="Partial" class="sr-only" />
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-warning mb-1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg>
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold">Partial</span>
            </label>
            
            <!-- Failed -->
            <label class="outcome-radio-label flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-3 border border-hairline/40 rounded-xl bg-canvas text-ink text-center hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 cursor-pointer active:scale-95 transition-all">
              <input type="radio" name="outcome" value="Failed" class="sr-only" />
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-error mb-1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold">Failed</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Failure context (Distraction reason selector) -->
        <div id="failed-context-panel" class="hidden space-y-2 animate-in slide-in-from-top-2 duration-200">
          <label for="failed-reason" class="block text-sm font-medium text-mute tracking-tight">What pulled you away from your flow?</label>
          <select id="failed-reason" class="w-full h-11 px-3 bg-canvas-soft border border-transparent rounded-sm text-sm text-ink focus:outline-none focus:bg-canvas focus:border-link/30 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-link/5 transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm">
            <option value="distraction">Distraction (social media, phone, messaging)</option>
            <option value="fatigue">Fatigue (brain fog, sleepiness, lack of energy)</option>
            <option value="goal-too-large">Scope issue (goal was too massive to finish)</option>
            <option value="interruption">External interruption (meeting, family, phone call)</option>
            <option value="unknown">Other / unspecified blocker</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <!-- Reflection notes -->
        <div class="space-y-1.5">
          <label for="reflection-notes" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-mute tracking-tight">Write down any thoughts, small wins, or feelings about this session (optional)</label>
          <textarea id="reflection-notes" rows="2" class="w-full p-3 bg-canvas-soft border border-transparent rounded-sm text-sm text-ink placeholder:text-mute/45 focus:outline-none focus:bg-canvas focus:border-link/30 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-link/5 transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm" placeholder="Share any thoughts on your energy, insights, or gentle wins…"></textarea>
        </div>

        <!-- Recovery Advisor Display -->
        <div id="modal-recovery-advisor" class="hidden p-3 bg-rose-500/[0.03] border border-dashed border-rose-500/25 rounded-sm text-xs text-ink leading-relaxed">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-rose-500 mb-1">A gentle nudge from your coach:</div>
          <div id="modal-recovery-text" class="text-body mt-0.5">Looking at what happened...</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Focus Forecast Attributor Section -->
        <div id="outcome-forecast-attribution" class="border border-hairline rounded-sm p-3 bg-canvas-soft-2/50 hidden space-y-2 select-none">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-body/80 tracking-tight">Log progress to goal</span>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 min-h-11 cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 -mx-3 -my-2">
              <input type="checkbox" id="sync-to-forecast" class="rounded border-hairline text-link focus:ring-link w-5 h-5 cursor-pointer" />
              <span class="text-xs font-mono font-bold text-ink">Sync Progress</span>
            </label>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-body" id="sync-goal-description">Add units to your active goal progress.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 sm:items-center">
            <div class="relative flex-grow">
              <input type="number" id="sync-forecast-value" min="0.1" step="any" class="w-full h-11 px-2 bg-canvas-soft border border-transparent rounded-sm text-sm text-ink focus:outline-none focus:bg-canvas focus:border-link/30 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-link/5 transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm" value="1" />
              <span id="sync-forecast-unit" class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-xs text-mute font-mono font-semibold">units</span>
            </div>
            <input type="text" id="sync-forecast-notes" autocomplete="off" class="w-full sm:w-2/3 h-11 px-2 bg-canvas-soft border border-transparent rounded-sm text-sm text-ink focus:outline-none focus:bg-canvas focus:border-link/30 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-link/5 transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm" placeholder="Log comments…" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Setbacks / difficult period support quote -->
        <div id="modal-why-matters-support" class="hidden p-3.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-warning/5 to-transparent border border-warning/20 rounded-sm text-xs leading-relaxed flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" class="text-warning shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4"/><path d="M12 16h.01"/></svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-warning tracking-tight block mb-0.5">Don't lose sight of your 'why':</span>
            <span id="modal-why-matters-support-text" class="text-body italic">Why Matters text</span>
            <span class="block text-xs text-mute mt-1 leading-relaxed">Every stumble is part of the climb. Be kind to yourself — each block of focus, no matter the outcome, builds the self-awareness that leads to lasting change.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="w-full h-11 bg-gradient-to-b from-link to-link/90 text-white hover:from-link-hover hover:to-link-hover/90 active:scale-[0.98] text-sm font-bold tracking-wide rounded-xl border-0 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-elevated">
          Save this reflection
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CELEBRATION SUMMARY OVERLAY (shown after completing a session) -->
  <div id="celebration-overlay" class="fixed inset-0 bg-canvas/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-[9999] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-sm bg-canvas border border-hairline/40 rounded-2xl shadow-elevated overflow-hidden animate-in fade-in zoom-in-95 duration-200 text-center">
